{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Believe me or not, I come offering a solution"},{"time":4000,"text":"to a very important part of this larger problem,"},{"time":8000,"text":"with the requisite focus on climate."},{"time":10000,"text":"And the solution I offer"},{"time":12000,"text":"is to the biggest culprit"},{"time":14000,"text":"in this massive mistreatment of the earth"},{"time":18000,"text":"by humankind,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and the resulting decline of the biosphere."},{"time":23000,"text":"That culprit is business and industry,"},{"time":26000,"text":"which happens to be where I have spent the last 52 years"},{"time":29000,"text":"since my graduation from Georgia Tech in 1956."},{"time":33000,"text":"As an industrial engineer,"},{"time":35000,"text":"cum aspiring and then successful entrepreneur."},{"time":39000,"text":"After founding my company, Interface, from scratch"},{"time":42000,"text":"in 1973, 36 years ago,"},{"time":45000,"text":"to produce carpet tiles in America"},{"time":47000,"text":"for the business and institution markets,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and shepherding it through start-up and survival"},{"time":53000,"text":"to prosperity and global dominance in its field,"},{"time":56000,"text":"I read Paul Hawken's book,"},{"time":58000,"text":"\"The Ecology of Commerce,\""},{"time":60000,"text":"the summer of 1994."},{"time":63000,"text":"In his book, Paul charges business and industry"},{"time":66000,"text":"as, one, the major culprit"},{"time":69000,"text":"in causing the decline of the biosphere,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and, two, the only institution that is large enough,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and pervasive enough, and powerful enough,"},{"time":76000,"text":"to really lead humankind out of this mess."},{"time":80000,"text":"And by the way he convicted me"},{"time":83000,"text":"as a plunderer of the earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"And I then challenged the people of Interface, my company,"},{"time":88000,"text":"to lead our company and the entire industrial world to sustainability,"},{"time":92000,"text":"which we defined as eventually operating"},{"time":94000,"text":"our petroleum-intensive company in such a way"},{"time":97000,"text":"as to take from the earth"},{"time":99000,"text":"only what can be renewed by the earth, naturally and rapidly --"},{"time":103000,"text":"not another fresh drop of oil --"},{"time":105000,"text":"and to do no harm to the biosphere."},{"time":109000,"text":"Take nothing: do no harm."},{"time":111000,"text":"I simply said, \"If Hawken is right"},{"time":113000,"text":"and business and industry must lead,"},{"time":115000,"text":"who will lead business and industry?"},{"time":117000,"text":"Unless somebody leads, nobody will.\""},{"time":120000,"text":"It's axiomatic. Why not us?"},{"time":123000,"text":"And thanks to the people of Interface,"},{"time":125000,"text":"I have become a recovering plunderer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"I once told a Fortune Magazine writer"},{"time":138000,"text":"that someday people like me would go to jail."},{"time":141000,"text":"And that became the headline of a Fortune article."},{"time":143000,"text":"They went on to describe me as America's greenest CEO."},{"time":147000,"text":"From plunderer to recovering plunderer,"},{"time":150000,"text":"to America's greenest CEO in five years --"},{"time":153000,"text":"that, frankly, was a pretty sad commentary"},{"time":155000,"text":"on American CEOs in 1999."},{"time":160000,"text":"Asked later in the Canadian documentary, \"The Corporation,\""},{"time":163000,"text":"what I meant by the \"go to jail\" remark,"},{"time":166000,"text":"I offered that theft is a crime."},{"time":170000,"text":"And theft of our children's future would someday be a crime."},{"time":175000,"text":"But I realized, for that to be true --"},{"time":177000,"text":"for theft of our children's future to be a crime --"},{"time":180000,"text":"there must be a clear, demonstrable alternative"},{"time":183000,"text":"to the take-make-waste industrial system"},{"time":186000,"text":"that so dominates our civilization,"},{"time":189000,"text":"and is the major culprit, stealing our children's future,"},{"time":192000,"text":"by digging up the earth"},{"time":194000,"text":"and converting it to products that quickly become waste"},{"time":198000,"text":"in a landfill or an incinerator --"},{"time":200000,"text":"in short, digging up the earth and converting it to pollution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"According to Paul and Anne Ehrlich"},{"time":207000,"text":"and a well-known environmental impact equation,"},{"time":210000,"text":"impact -- a bad thing --"},{"time":212000,"text":"is the product of population, affluence and technology."},{"time":216000,"text":"That is, impact is generated by people,"},{"time":220000,"text":"what they consume in their affluence,"},{"time":222000,"text":"and how it is produced."},{"time":225000,"text":"And though the equation is largely subjective,"},{"time":227000,"text":"you can perhaps quantify people, and perhaps quantify affluence,"},{"time":231000,"text":"but technology is abusive in too many ways to quantify."},{"time":235000,"text":"So the equation is conceptual."},{"time":237000,"text":"Still it works to help us understand the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240000,"text":"So we set out at Interface, in 1994,"},{"time":245000,"text":"to create an example:"},{"time":247000,"text":"to transform the way we made carpet,"},{"time":249000,"text":"a petroleum-intensive product for materials as well as energy,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and to transform our technologies"},{"time":255000,"text":"so they diminished environmental impact,"},{"time":258000,"text":"rather than multiplied it."},{"time":261000,"text":"Paul and Anne Ehrlich's environmental impact equation:"},{"time":264000,"text":"I is equal to P times A times T:"},{"time":267000,"text":"population, affluence and technology."},{"time":270000,"text":"I wanted Interface to rewrite that equation so that it read"},{"time":276000,"text":"I equals P times A divided by T."},{"time":279000,"text":"Now, the mathematically-minded will see immediately"},{"time":282000,"text":"that T in the numerator increases impact -- a bad thing --"},{"time":285000,"text":"but T in the denominator decreases impact."},{"time":289000,"text":"So I ask, \"What would move T, technology,"},{"time":293000,"text":"from the numerator -- call it T1 --"},{"time":295000,"text":"where it increases impact,"},{"time":297000,"text":"to the denominator -- call it T2 --"},{"time":300000,"text":"where it reduces impact?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":303000,"text":"I thought about the characteristics"},{"time":307000,"text":"of first industrial revolution,"},{"time":309000,"text":"T1, as we practiced it at Interface,"},{"time":312000,"text":"and it had the following characteristics."},{"time":316000,"text":"Extractive: taking raw materials from the earth."},{"time":320000,"text":"Linear: take, make, waste."},{"time":323000,"text":"Powered by fossil fuel-derived energy."},{"time":325000,"text":"Wasteful: abusive and focused on labor productivity."},{"time":329000,"text":"More carpet per man-hour."},{"time":332000,"text":"Thinking it through, I realized that all those attributes"},{"time":335000,"text":"must be changed to move T to the denominator."},{"time":340000,"text":"In the new industrial revolution extractive must be replaced by renewable;"},{"time":345000,"text":"linear by cyclical;"},{"time":347000,"text":"fossil fuel energy by renewable energy, sunlight;"},{"time":351000,"text":"wasteful by waste-free;"},{"time":353000,"text":"and abusive by benign;"},{"time":355000,"text":"and labor productivity by resource productivity."},{"time":359000,"text":"And I reasoned that if we could make those transformative changes,"},{"time":363000,"text":"and get rid of T1 altogether,"},{"time":365000,"text":"we could reduce our impact to zero,"},{"time":368000,"text":"including our impact on the climate."},{"time":371000,"text":"And that became the Interface plan in 1995,"},{"time":374000,"text":"and has been the plan ever since."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377000,"text":"We have measured our progress very rigorously."},{"time":381000,"text":"So I can tell you how far we have come in the ensuing 12 years."},{"time":385000,"text":"Net greenhouse gas emissions"},{"time":387000,"text":"down 82 percent in absolute tonnage."},{"time":391000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":395000,"text":"Over the same span of time"},{"time":397000,"text":"sales have increased by two-thirds and profits have doubled."},{"time":400000,"text":"So an 82 percent absolute reduction"},{"time":403000,"text":"translates into a 90 percent reduction"},{"time":405000,"text":"in greenhouse gas intensity relative to sales."},{"time":409000,"text":"This is the magnitude"},{"time":411000,"text":"of the reduction the entire global technosphere"},{"time":414000,"text":"must realize by 2050"},{"time":417000,"text":"to avoid catastrophic climate disruption --"},{"time":420000,"text":"so the scientists are telling us."},{"time":423000,"text":"Fossil fuel usage is down 60 percent per unit of production,"},{"time":427000,"text":"due to efficiencies in renewables."},{"time":429000,"text":"The cheapest, most secure barrel of oil there is"},{"time":432000,"text":"is the one not used through efficiencies."},{"time":435000,"text":"Water usage is down 75 percent"},{"time":438000,"text":"in our worldwide carpet tile business."},{"time":440000,"text":"Down 40 percent in our broadloom carpet business,"},{"time":443000,"text":"which we acquired in 1993"},{"time":445000,"text":"right here in California, City of Industry,"},{"time":447000,"text":"where water is so precious."},{"time":450000,"text":"Renewable or recyclable materials are 25 percent of the total, and growing rapidly."},{"time":454000,"text":"Renewable energy is 27 percent of our total,"},{"time":457000,"text":"going for 100 percent."},{"time":459000,"text":"We have diverted 148 million pounds --"},{"time":462000,"text":"that's 74,000 tons --"},{"time":464000,"text":"of used carpet from landfills,"},{"time":467000,"text":"closing the loop on material flows"},{"time":469000,"text":"through reverse logistics"},{"time":471000,"text":"and post-consumer recycling technologies"},{"time":474000,"text":"that did not exist when we started 14 years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478000,"text":"Those new cyclical technologies"},{"time":480000,"text":"have contributed mightily to the fact that we have produced and sold"},{"time":483000,"text":"85 million square yards of climate-neutral carpet"},{"time":487000,"text":"since 2004,"},{"time":489000,"text":"meaning no net contribution to global climate disruption"},{"time":493000,"text":"in producing the carpet throughout the supply chain,"},{"time":495000,"text":"from mine and well head clear to end-of-life reclamation --"},{"time":500000,"text":"independent third-party certified."},{"time":502000,"text":"We call it Cool Carpet."},{"time":505000,"text":"And it has been a powerful marketplace differentiator,"},{"time":508000,"text":"increasing sales and profits."},{"time":510000,"text":"Three years ago we launched carpet tile for the home,"},{"time":514000,"text":"under the brand Flor,"},{"time":516000,"text":"misspelled F-L-O-R."},{"time":519000,"text":"You can point and click today at Flor.com"},{"time":521000,"text":"and have Cool Carpet delivered to your front door in five days."},{"time":525000,"text":"It is practical, and pretty too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535000,"text":"We reckon that we are a bit over halfway"},{"time":537000,"text":"to our goal: zero impact, zero footprint."},{"time":542000,"text":"We've set 2020 as our target year for zero,"},{"time":545000,"text":"for reaching the top, the summit of Mount Sustainability."},{"time":550000,"text":"We call this Mission Zero."},{"time":552000,"text":"And this is perhaps the most important facet:"},{"time":555000,"text":"we have found Mission Zero to be incredibly good for business."},{"time":559000,"text":"A better business model,"},{"time":562000,"text":"a better way to bigger profits."},{"time":564000,"text":"Here is the business case for sustainability."},{"time":567000,"text":"From real life experience, costs are down, not up,"},{"time":571000,"text":"reflecting some 400 million dollars"},{"time":573000,"text":"of avoided costs in pursuit of zero waste --"},{"time":577000,"text":"the first face of Mount Sustainability."},{"time":580000,"text":"This has paid all the costs for the transformation of Interface."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584000,"text":"And this dispels a myth too,"},{"time":586000,"text":"this false choice between the environment and the economy."},{"time":590000,"text":"Our products are the best they've ever been,"},{"time":592000,"text":"inspired by design for sustainability,"},{"time":594000,"text":"an unexpected wellspring of innovation."},{"time":598000,"text":"Our people are galvanized around this shared higher purpose."},{"time":601000,"text":"You cannot beat it for attracting the best people"},{"time":603000,"text":"and bringing them together."},{"time":606000,"text":"And the goodwill of the marketplace is astonishing."},{"time":609000,"text":"No amount of advertising, no clever marketing campaign,"},{"time":613000,"text":"at any price, could have produced or created"},{"time":616000,"text":"this much goodwill."},{"time":619000,"text":"Costs, products, people, marketplaces --"},{"time":621000,"text":"what else is there?"},{"time":623000,"text":"It is a better business model."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"And here is our 14-year record of sales and profits."},{"time":630000,"text":"There is a dip there, from 2001 to 2003:"},{"time":633000,"text":"a dip when our sales, over a three-year period,"},{"time":635000,"text":"were down 17 percent."},{"time":637000,"text":"But the marketplace was down 36 percent."},{"time":640000,"text":"We literally gained market share."},{"time":642000,"text":"We might not have survived that recession"},{"time":645000,"text":"but for the advantages of sustainability."},{"time":648000,"text":"If every business were pursuing Interface plans,"},{"time":652000,"text":"would that solve all our problems?"},{"time":654000,"text":"I don't think so."},{"time":656000,"text":"I remain troubled by the revised Ehrlich equation,"},{"time":659000,"text":"I equals P times A divided by T2."},{"time":663000,"text":"That A is a capital A,"},{"time":665000,"text":"suggesting that affluence is an end in itself."},{"time":670000,"text":"But what if we reframed Ehrlich further?"},{"time":674000,"text":"And what if we made A a lowercase 'a,'"},{"time":677000,"text":"suggesting that it is a means to an end,"},{"time":679000,"text":"and that end is happiness --"},{"time":682000,"text":"more happiness with less stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":685000,"text":"You know that would reframe civilization itself --"},{"time":688000,"text":"(Applause) --"},{"time":696000,"text":"and our whole system of economics,"},{"time":699000,"text":"if not for our species, then perhaps for the one that succeeds us:"},{"time":705000,"text":"the sustainable species, living on a finite earth,"},{"time":708000,"text":"ethically, happily and ecologically"},{"time":711000,"text":"in balance with nature"},{"time":713000,"text":"and all her natural systems for a thousand generations,"},{"time":716000,"text":"or 10,000 generations --"},{"time":718000,"text":"that is to say, into the indefinite future."},{"time":721000,"text":"But does the earth have to wait for our extinction as a species?"},{"time":726000,"text":"Well maybe so. But I don't think so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"At Interface we really intend to bring this prototypical"},{"time":732000,"text":"sustainable, zero-footprint industrial company"},{"time":735000,"text":"fully into existence by 2020."},{"time":738000,"text":"We can see our way now,"},{"time":740000,"text":"clear to the top of that mountain."},{"time":742000,"text":"And now the challenge is in execution."},{"time":745000,"text":"And as my good friend and adviser Amory Lovins says,"},{"time":748000,"text":"\"If something exists, it must be possible.\""},{"time":752000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":755000,"text":"If we can actually do it, it must be possible."},{"time":758000,"text":"If we, a petro-intensive company can do it, anybody can."},{"time":762000,"text":"And if anybody can, it follows that everybody can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"Hawken fulfilled business and industry,"},{"time":769000,"text":"leading humankind away from the abyss"},{"time":773000,"text":"because, with continued unchecked decline of the biosphere,"},{"time":778000,"text":"a very dear person is at risk here --"},{"time":781000,"text":"frankly, an unacceptable risk."},{"time":783000,"text":"Who is that person?"},{"time":785000,"text":"Not you. Not I."},{"time":787000,"text":"But let me introduce you to the one who is most at risk here."},{"time":790000,"text":"And I myself met this person in the early days of this mountain climb."},{"time":794000,"text":"On a Tuesday morning in March of 1996,"},{"time":798000,"text":"I was talking to people, as I did at every opportunity back then,"},{"time":801000,"text":"bringing them along and often not knowing whether I was connecting."},{"time":805000,"text":"But about five days later back in Atlanta,"},{"time":808000,"text":"I received an email from Glenn Thomas,"},{"time":811000,"text":"one of my people in the California meeting."},{"time":813000,"text":"He was sending me an original poem"},{"time":815000,"text":"that he had composed after our Tuesday morning together."},{"time":818000,"text":"And when I read it it was one of the most uplifting moments of my life."},{"time":822000,"text":"Because it told me, by God, one person got it."},{"time":826000,"text":"Here is what Glenn wrote. And here is that person, most at risk."},{"time":830000,"text":"Please meet \"Tomorrow's Child.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":834000,"text":"\"Without a name, an unseen face, and knowing not your time or place,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"Tomorrow's child, though yet unborn,"},{"time":841000,"text":"I met you first last Tuesday morn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844000,"text":"A wise friend introduced us two."},{"time":846000,"text":"And through his sobering point of view"}]},{"cues":[{"time":848000,"text":"I saw a day that you would see, a day for you but not for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":853000,"text":"Knowing you has changed my thinking."},{"time":855000,"text":"For I never had an inkling"}]},{"cues":[{"time":857000,"text":"that perhaps the things I do might someday,"},{"time":860000,"text":"somehow threaten you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":863000,"text":"Tomorrow's child, my daughter, son,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":865000,"text":"I'm afraid I've just begun to think of you and of your good,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"though always having known I should."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871000,"text":"Begin, I will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":873000,"text":"The way the cost of what I squander, what is lost,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":876000,"text":"if ever I forget that you"},{"time":878000,"text":"will someday come and live here too.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":882000,"text":"Well, every day of my life since,"},{"time":884000,"text":"\"Tomorrow's Child\" has spoken to me"},{"time":886000,"text":"with one simple but profound message,"},{"time":888000,"text":"which I presume to share with you."},{"time":890000,"text":"We are, each and every one,"},{"time":892000,"text":"a part of the web of life."},{"time":895000,"text":"The continuum of humanity, sure, but in a larger sense, the web of life itself."},{"time":899000,"text":"And we have a choice to make"},{"time":901000,"text":"during our brief, brief visit"},{"time":903000,"text":"to this beautiful blue and green living planet:"},{"time":907000,"text":"to hurt it or to help it."},{"time":910000,"text":"For you, it's your call."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":915000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}